comments: Absolutely. Professor Marcus is incredible and taking her class was such a joy this semester; the syllabus is filled with fascinating films and her course shed light on the accompanying texts in a way that made the class feel more engaging than any other Ive taken during my time at Yale. I only wish I could take it again!
